dcterms:description: This dataset consists of key performance indicators (KPIs) regarding network and devices, including types of devices (IoT-based devices, smartphones, URLLC devices, etc.), user equipment (UE) category, maximum packet loss, QoS class identifier (QCI), packet delay budget, day and time information, and weather conditions.
dcterms:title: Dataset of key performance indicators (KPIs) regarding network and devices
